KCC First Introduction: KuCoin Community Chain (KCC) is a high-performance and decentralized public chain built by the fans of KCS and KuCoin.
KCC Second Introduction: Its purpose is to solve the problems such as low performance and high cost of public chain, So as to provide Community users with more high-speed, convenient and low-cost experience Of blockchain.
KCC INTRODUCE 1: Fully compatible with Ethereum and ERC-20 smart contracts, With extremely low migration costs
KCC INTRODUCE 2: KuCoin Token (KCS) will serve as the only core fuel and native token for KCC and can be used in scenarios such as gas fee payment
KCC INTRODUCE 3: A block every 3 seconds results in faster transaction confirmation and higher chain performance
KCC INTRODUCE 4: Proof of Staked Authority (PoSA) consensus algorithm, high efficiency, security and stability
